发信人: Ashora (邪神阿修罗--当西藏不再神秘), 信区: Career_MNC
标  题: BE:Recruiting Assistant (上海市) 
发信站: 水木社区 (Thu Jul  7 18:16:15 2005), 站内
Job Responsibilities: 
・ Assist recruiters in sourcing candidates and initial CV screening; 
・ Provide administrative support during the recruiting process, such as data input to the IRIS system, arranging interviews with the candidates, updating latest recruiting status report, as well as document filing; 
・ Be responsible for managing job posting on Internet; 
・ Conduct name finding and headhunting calls based on the recruiters’ guidance and relevant business hiring needs; 
・ Act as a coordinator between internal clients and external candidates regarding interview schedule, feedback collection, and communication with the candidates during the on-board process; 
・ Coordinate with the HR team with reference to candidates’ on-board; 
・ Be responsible for campus recruiting arrangement and document preparation, including sending interview invitations, contacting schools, maintain candidates information in the system; 
・ Track monthly ERP (Employee Referral Program) progress, and coordinate with the HR staff in terms of ERP bonus. 
Job Requirements: 
・ Bachelor Degree or above; 
・ Minimum a year experience in recruiting with multinational companies; 
・ Familiar with various recruiting channels is preferred 
・ Good understanding of overall human resources operation 
・ Good English language ability (Oral, listening, reading and writing) 
・ Proficient in computer and MS Office 
